{"tid":2322353,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Pay 被指封閉 NFC 技術 荷蘭展開反壟斷調查","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:39:27.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"203e9d8cfac290d53f1ed5f0722b75591966f635","tid":2322353,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"歐盟委員會在半年前正式向 Apple 開展反壟斷調查，評估 Apple Pay 推行是否違反了歐盟競爭法（Competition Law），而 Apple 在應付歐盟同時，荷蘭反壟斷監管機構亦同時對其展開審查，目前正調查用戶是否可以自由選擇通過非接觸式付款時使用的金融App。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭消費者和市場管理局周五（11 日）表示，已開始對支付 App 是否可以進行 NFC 技術進行調查。該機構指某些智能電話僅允許 App 開發商自己的支付 App 連接到 NFC 通信，其雖未有明指 Apple，但目前只有 iPhone 以及 Apple Watch 用戶必須要使用 Apple Pay 才可在其移動設備上使用 NFC 技術⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/12/apple-pay-5/software/ios-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F12%2Fapple-pay-5%2Fsoftware%2Fios-app%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcvkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=e4341bef\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/12/apple-pay-5/software/ios-app/</a>"},{"pid":"d6079a73dc05df3ba9f8fb0bdbc703fdb32a58da","tid":2322353,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"啲歐洲國家真係好鐘意冇錢就搵科技公司開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0f3e84a869d1f55dd0b92b435edc30ad5318e8","tid":2322353,"uid":215621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:23:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40315fa5be26024aea87c408ab1594ecb9465612","tid":2322353,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6079a73dc05df3ba9f8fb0bdbc703fdb32a58da","tid":2322353,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:13:47.000Z","msg":"啲歐洲國家真係好鐘意冇錢就搵科技公司開刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"咁唔通搵自己國家嘅公司開刀咩<br />\n梗係搵外資開刀"}]}